_sText: This is our first map, so please bare with us. This map started as going to be a de map, but as we got further into it, we decided, this is more of a fight yard. It only took us a couple hours to do this much, but we do plan on making other versions of this. I also, have the file in there so that you can edit it yourself. I would like to see what people can do with this map. If you do edit, please keep the =PA=, but you may add your name if you want.  Thanks.
